Name: hadith
Description: Hadith tools (Bukhari/Muslim).
Version: 1.0

Commands:
- hadith_get
  Get a hadith by collection and number.
  Parameters:
  - collection (string, required): bukhari|muslim
  - number (integer, required)

- hadith_search
  Search hadith in a collection.
  Parameters:
  - collection (string, required)
  - query (string, required)
  - page (integer, optional)
  - per_page (integer, optional)

- hadith_collections
  List available collections from API source.

Data:
- Uses local JSON datasets under app/database/hadith/*.json
